fulltitle: Robert McNamara on John F. Kennedy and Vietnam Withdrawal

Robert McNamara, Secretary of Defense to John F. Kennedy and Lyndon B. Johnson during the Vietnam War, discusses Kennedy's attitude towards the withdrawal of troops from that country.
